NK013(pa)013:0: sh+r+ai gu h+ya ga r+b+ha s+ya pa ra spa rah ra t+na na p+r+aa r+tha na tsa /
NK013(pa)013:1: m+aa rga kra ma pra ni d+h+aa na d+gu ti
NK013(pa)013:2: su me g+he na p+au sh+pam n+aa ma b+hi ha
NK013(pa)013:4: dpal gsang ba snying po'i brgyud pa rin po che la gsol ba 'debs pa dang /
NK013(pa)013:5: lam rim smon lam phun tshogs dpag bsam sprin gyi me tog ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)013:6: ka dag kun bzang gdod nas ye sangs rgyas /
NK013(pa)013:8: / 'khor 'das mnyam nyid gnyis med klong du gyur //
NK013(pa)013:9: dang po'i sangs rgyas dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK013(pa)013:10: gsang bdag chen po khyed la mi phyed 'dud //
NK013(pa)013:11: rgyal sras dbang phyug mthu stobs nus pa'i gter //
NK013(pa)013:12: sangs rgyas stong gi bstan pa 'dzin byed cing //
NK013(pa)013:13: gdul dka' 'dul mdzad phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK013(pa)013:14: gsang bdag gnyis pa'i zhabs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK013(pa)013:15: thub pas lung bstan o rgyan d+aak+ki'i gtso //
NK013(pa)013:16: gsang sngags rgyud sde zab mo'i mdzod 'chang ba //
NK013(pa)013:17: rin chen mang gi rnam 'phrul thams cad mkhyen //
NK013(pa)013:18: ku ku r+aa dza'i zhabs la rgyal ba'i dngos slob ma 'ongs lung bstan pa //
NK013(pa)013:19: chos kyi rgyal po nges don rgya mtsho'i bdag /
NK013(pa)013:20: tshe gcig sangs rgyas sa la gshegs mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)013:21: in+t+ra b+hu ti'i zhabs la gsung rab rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i pha rol phyin //
NK013(pa)013:22: don bcud gsang sngags zab mo'i gnas lugs rtogs /
NK013(pa)013:24: / 'dod yon spang med rnam dag lam du khyer //
NK013(pa)013:25: sh+aakya su tri'i zhabs gsung rab rgya mtsho'i gzhung don khong du chud //
NK013(pa)013:26: ka dag gnas lugs rang byung 'gyur med rtogs //
NK013(pa)013:27: phung khams lhar smin stobs kyis pha rol son //
NK013(pa)013:28: sa brgyad sems ma'i zhabs la theg chen rnal 'byor gsang sngags zab mo'i bdag /
NK013(pa)013:29: bla med rdo rje theg pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK013(pa)013:30: tshe gcig tshe 'dir rig 'dzin mchog thob pa //
NK013(pa)013:31: rdo rje yon tan gzungs la gsol yang dag thugs kyi sgor zhugs dngos grub brnyes //
NK013(pa)013:32: mi 'gyur bde stong dbyer med rdo rje 'dzin //
NK013(pa)013:33: zab lam bstan pa'i mnga' bdag chos kyi rje //
NK013(pa)013:34: grub chen h'u ka ra la gsang sngags phyi nang chos la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK013(pa)013:35: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs rnams zhal gzigs nas //
NK013(pa)013:36: sna tshogs thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)013:37: phra chen ha sti'i zhabs la gsol 'jam dpal dbyangs kyis thugs rjes rjes bzung nas //
NK013(pa)013:38: phyi nang theg pa'i chos rnams thugs la rdzogs //
NK013(pa)013:39: ngo mtshar gzhung dang gdams pa du ma'i gter //
NK013(pa)013:40: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhabs 'od dpag med kyi rnam 'phrul 'chi med sku //
NK013(pa)013:41: d+ha na ko sha'i mtsho gling pad+mara skyes //
NK013(pa)013:42: sangs rgyas gnyis pa zab rgyas chos gter bdag /
NK013(pa)013:43: u rgyan pad+ma'i zhabs la pan chen du ma tshogs pa'i dbus na mdzes //
NK013(pa)013:44: rig pa'i gnas lnga ma lus thugs la rdzogs //
NK013(pa)013:45: rgya gar mkhas pa'i mchog gyur bka' drin bdag /
NK013(pa)013:46: dri med bshes gnyen zhabs lung rigs gsung gi dbang phyug mnga' brnyes shing //
NK013(pa)013:47: pha rol smra ba'i log rtog tshar gcod cing //
NK013(pa)013:48: zab rgyas chos kyi rgya mtsho bsgyur mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)013:49: lo tsa rin chen mchog la thub dbang bstan pa'i rgyu 'bras theg pa la //
NK013(pa)013:50: ji bzhin ma nor mngon sum rtogs gyur nas //
NK013(pa)013:51: zag med dgongs pa mchog la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK013(pa)013:52: kye ru mchog skyong zhabs rnam dag thos pa'i lung chos thugs la rdzogs //
NK013(pa)013:53: gsang sngags zab mo'i bsgrub rgyud bstan pa 'dzin //
NK013(pa)013:54: zag med zung 'jug mngon sum rtogs pa yi //
NK013(pa)013:55: rgyal ba yon tan zhabs la thub dbang bstan pa'i dpal la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK013(pa)013:56: mi 'gyur ye shes go 'phang mchog thob nas //
NK013(pa)013:57: lus can theg mchog lam la bkod mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)013:58: ye shes rin chen zhabs mkhyen rab stong nyid rgya mtsho chen po las //
NK013(pa)013:60: 'gags med snying rje'i rlabs chen kun nas g.yos //
NK013(pa)013:61: gsang sngags zab don rin chen 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK013(pa)013:62: sras kyi dam pa khu lung ba /
NK013(pa)013:63: yon tan rgya mtsho'i zhabs la de gnub nyid sku yi sras gyur gsang sngags 'dzin //
NK013(pa)013:64: rab 'byams bstan pa'i srog shing mdzod gsum bdag /
NK013(pa)013:65: tshad med thugs rjes bslab bya gting nas rdzogs //
NK013(pa)013:66: ye shes rgya mtsho'i zhabs la gsang sngags zab mo'i gnas lugs khong du chud //
NK013(pa)013:67: yang phur sman gsum rgyud lung man ngag bcas //
NK013(pa)013:68: mkhas grub gnyis kyi rgyal rgyud 'dzin mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)013:69: blo gros byang chub zhabs la sgyu 'phrul theg pa'i chos la dbang thob nas //
NK013(pa)013:70: nyon mongs ye shes chen por lam du khyer //
NK013(pa)013:71: gsang sngags mnga' brnyes bstan 'dzin chos kyi rje //
NK013(pa)013:73: sh+aakya 'byung gnas zhabs la bskal mang sngon nas sbyangs pa zhib pa'i mthus //
NK013(pa)013:74: theg mchog bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis don rtogs nas //
NK013(pa)013:75: bdag gzhan mchog gi don la sbyar mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)013:76: zur chung shes rab grags pa la gnas kyi khyad 'phags rke lung zhes bya der //
NK013(pa)013:77: mdo bzhi sngo lnga la sogs gsang sngags chos //
NK013(pa)013:78: ma lus thugs su chud nas bsgrub pa mdzad //
NK013(pa)013:79: yang khyed bla ma'i zhabs la gzhung lugs rab 'byams don la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK013(pa)013:80: gdul bya mtha' dag theg pa'i lam la gzud //
NK013(pa)013:81: sangs rgyas bstan pa rgya cher spel mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)013:83: sh+aakya seng ge'i zhabs theg pa mtha' dag khong chud rdzogs chen don //
NK013(pa)013:84: ji bzhin rtogs nas gzung 'dzin rang sar grol //
NK013(pa)013:85: bdag gzhan don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'i dpal /
NK013(pa)013:88: rdzogs chen pa zhes grags la rgya gar yul du byang chub sems sbyangs nas //
NK013(pa)013:89: gangs can khrod 'dir gsang sngags bstan pa skyongs //
NK013(pa)013:90: bde ba can du rgyal sras byang chub sems //
NK013(pa)013:91: sa bcu'i dbang phyug dam pa de la 'dud //
NK013(pa)013:92: lung rigs man ngag kun la mkhas gyur nas //
NK013(pa)013:93: mdo rgyud dgongs pa'i thugs la nyi ma shar //
NK013(pa)013:94: bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyis bdag gzhan rgyud sbyangs pa //
NK013(pa)013:95: chos rjes gtsang ston zhabs la chos nyid rnam dag byams pa'i ri bo la //
NK013(pa)013:96: snying rje'i 'bras ldan dpag bsam 'bum gyis brgyan //
NK013(pa)013:97: mtshan mchog don ldan 'gro mgon chos kyi rje //
NK013(pa)013:98: byams pa chen po'i zhabs la snang stong gnyis med chos dbyings nam mkha' la //
NK013(pa)013:99: gnas lugs 'gyur med rang byung rdo rje'i sku //
NK013(pa)013:100: lung bstan mchod thob tsa sde spyan snga ba //
NK013(pa)013:101: nam mkha' rdo rje'i zhabs la rgyud sde bsrung zhing gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin //
NK013(pa)013:102: thos bsam sgom pa'i bya ba mthar phyin nas /
NK013(pa)013:104: / 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i don la ma rmongs pa //
NK013(pa)013:105: thugs rje ye shes zhabs la ldem dgongs brgyad dang mtha' drug tshul bzhi dang //
NK013(pa)013:106: rton pa bzhi dang gzhung gi 'bod len gyis //
NK013(pa)013:107: gsang sngags zab mo'i rgyud gzhung gtan la dbab //
NK013(pa)013:108: ston pa dbang 'byor zhabs la dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por bskyil //
NK013(pa)013:109: lung rigs dri med pad+mo'i kha phye nas //
NK013(pa)013:110: blo gsal rkang drug ldan la dga' ston 'gyed //
NK013(pa)013:111: rje btsun dpal 'bar zhabs la kun mkhyen zag spangs bstan pa'i mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK013(pa)013:112: sdom gsum rnam dag nyes ltung dri mas dben //
NK013(pa)013:113: mtshungs med chos rje gdul bya'i mgon gyur pa //
NK013(pa)013:114: ston pa mgon rgyal zhabs la dri med tshul khrims rnam dag rgyal ba'i mtshan //
NK013(pa)013:115: theg mchog zab don ma lus thugs su chud //
NK013(pa)013:116: mkhyen rab 'jam dpal dbyangs dang gnyis med pa //
NK013(pa)013:118: tshul khrims rgyal mtshan zhabs la mkhas pa rgya mtsho tshogs pa'i dbus na mdzes //
NK013(pa)013:119: sna tshogs theg pa'i gzhung lugs bshad rtsal che //
NK013(pa)013:120: rang 'dod med cing gzhan phan kho nar sems //
NK013(pa)013:122: d+h+aarma kla k+sha'i zhabs la mdo sngags rgya mtsho'i dbus su legs 'khrungs shing //
NK013(pa)013:123: gsung rab pad+mo'i mnga' bdag chos kyi rje //
NK013(pa)013:124: don bcu sbrang rtsi lta bu'i mnga' bdag can //
NK013(pa)013:126: ye shes rgyal mtshan zhabs la mang thos gsung rab kun gyi mthar son cing //
NK013(pa)013:127: rgyal ba'i dbang po ji bzhin mkhyen gyur nas //
NK013(pa)013:128: mkhas mchog rnams kyi gtsug gi rgyan gyur pa //
NK013(pa)013:129: dpal 'bar drung ba nam mkha' rgyal mtshan zhabs la gzhung lugs rgya mtsho'i gling na yon tan gyi //
NK013(pa)013:130: gdengs ka rab 'bar stong nyid phugs sgra sgrogs //
NK013(pa)013:131: blo gros klu dbang tshul khrims nor bu'i gter //
NK013(pa)013:133: nam mkha' dpal ba'i rab dkar mkhyen pa'i sa gzhi yangs pa la //
NK013(pa)013:134: thugs rjes dpag bsam 'dod 'byung kho lags yangs //
NK013(pa)013:135: nus pa mi zad gter mnga' 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK013(pa)013:136: nam mkha' rgya mtsho'i zhabs la gting mtha' bral ba chos nyid bden don gzigs //
NK013(pa)013:137: lung rtogs yon tan nor bu'i mdzod 'chang ba //
NK013(pa)013:138: sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa'i bla ma brnyes //
NK013(pa)013:140: chos kyi dbang pa'i zhabs la sh+aakya'i bstan pa chu gtor kha ba dkar po bsrubs pa las //
NK013(pa)013:141: don gnyis bsil zer stong 'phro snyigs dus skyabs //
NK013(pa)013:142: mtha' klas rgyud pa'i mun sel ri bong 'dzin //
NK013(pa)013:143: pu nya badz+ra'i zhabs la skyon bral bslab pa gsum gyis rgyud phyug cing //
NK013(pa)013:144: dri bral bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi don gzigs nas //
NK013(pa)013:145: sgrib bral sku gsum dgongs pa mngon gyur pa //
NK013(pa)013:147: chos kyi 'byung gnas zhabs la pad+ma'i gsang bstan phyogs brgyar spel ba la //
NK013(pa)013:148: tshad med thugs rjes dgongs pa'i dpal thob cing //
NK013(pa)013:149: gsang sngags snga 'gyur chos la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK013(pa)013:150: stag bu shakya bkra shis zhabs bka' gter gzhung la mkhyen pa'i spyan ras yangs //
NK013(pa)013:151: don brgyud yid bzhin nor bu bdag gir thob //
NK013(pa)013:152: lta dgongs rnam dag thugs rje mtshungs pa med //
NK013(pa)013:154: rin chen rdo rje'i zhabs chos kun mthar thug zab lam rdzogs pa che'i //
NK013(pa)013:155: rtogs pas rgyud phyug rim gnyis gdengs dang ldan //
NK013(pa)013:156: pad+mas rjes bzung ye shes chen po brnyes //
NK013(pa)013:158: bud+ha mang+ga'i zhabs la rin chen byang chub sems la brtan pa thob //
NK013(pa)013:159: dbang gdams man ngag mang pos thugs rgyud khengs //
NK013(pa)013:160: bskyed rdzogs bsnyen bsgrub mang po'i pha rol son //
NK013(pa)013:162: sh+aakya tshe ring zhabs la nang du rim gnyis rtogs pa brtan gyur kyang //
NK013(pa)013:163: sbas pa'i tshul gyis sgrub pa mtha' ru bskyol //
NK013(pa)013:164: zab chos 'di las rtogs pa mchog brnyes pa //
NK013(pa)013:166: u rgyan phun tshogs zhabs mdo sngags grub mtha' rgya mtsho'i pha rol son //
NK013(pa)013:167: rgya chen rgyud sde'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur //
NK013(pa)013:168: bde stong nyams kyis sgegs pa'i he ru ka /
NK013(pa)013:169: thugs kyi rdo rje'i zhabs nges 'byung chen pos chos brgyad mgo snyoms shing //
NK013(pa)013:170: snying rje chen pos byang chub thugs 'byongs te //
NK013(pa)013:171: ye shes chen pos snang srid sgyu mar gzigs //
NK013(pa)013:172: blo gros chen po'i zhabs rmad byung legs bshad gsung gi nyi 'od kyis //
NK013(pa)013:173: rmongs pa'i rab rib kun nas 'phrog byed cing //
NK013(pa)013:174: skal bzang thar pa'i pad tshal rgyas byed pa //
NK013(pa)013:175: dpal ldan bla ma'i zhabs 'bar des rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dang //
NK013(pa)013:176: gnas yul zhing sngags lhan skyes d+aak+ki'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)013:177: bstan srung ma mgon gnod sbyin lcam dral la //
NK013(pa)013:178: mos gus gdung bas gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal lo /
NK013(pa)013:180: / 'di ltar snang grags lha yi ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)013:181: gzhi yi sangs rgyas sems can thams cad dang //
NK013(pa)013:182: gsang sngags sgor zhugs gsang ba'i dam tshig can //
NK013(pa)013:183: rdo rje'i mched bcas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lor //
NK013(pa)013:184: rdo rje mchog gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i gshis //
NK013(pa)013:185: bya rtsol bral ba bde chen snying po la //
NK013(pa)013:186: rang bab bzhag pa bcos slad kun bral bar //
NK013(pa)013:187: rang ngo shes pa'i ngang nas gsol ba 'debs //
NK013(pa)013:188: de ltar dpal ldan brgyud gsum bla ma ltar //
NK013(pa)013:189: byang chub bar du skyabs mchi gsol 'debs na //
NK013(pa)013:190: lam bzang bsgrub pa'i 'gal rkyen kun zhi zhing //
NK013(pa)013:191: mthun rkyen smon pa'i don kun 'grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)013:192: shin tu rnyed daka'i dal rten yid bzhin nor //
NK013(pa)013:193: thob dka' 'jigs sla chu yi lbu ba ltar //
NK013(pa)013:194: yid brtan mi rung srid pa'i bde ba la //
NK013(pa)013:195: zhena pa snying nasa ldog para byin gyis rlobs /
NK013(pa)013:197: / 'jigs rung 'khor ba'i me 'obs nyams nga bar //
NK013(pa)013:198: gang+g+aa'i chu ltar bsil ba'i log shes kyis //
NK013(pa)013:199: thar med dus ring lasa kyis manra ba'i 'gror //
NK013(pa)013:200: shin tu snying rje chena posa yid drangs te //
NK013(pa)013:201: skyabs gansa rina chena gsuma gyi gdugsa dakara dabubs //
NK013(pa)013:202: phan bde'i 'dod pa 'jo ba'i ngal 'tsho thob //
NK013(pa)013:203: rlabsa chen byang chub semas dang rgyal sras kyi //
NK013(pa)013:204: spyod pa rgya mtsho 'byongs para byin gyis rlobs //
NK013(pa)013:205: gsang chen gnyis med mthar thug lung gi spyi //
NK013(pa)013:206: rgyud chen dapala ldana sgyu 'phrul gasnga snying sgor //
NK013(pa)013:207: don chen tshe 'dir 'grub pa'i thabs gcig pu //
NK013(pa)013:208: brtse chen matshana nyid brgyad ldana bla ma lasa //
NK013(pa)013:209: sangs rgyas las kyang dkon pa'i rdo rje'i theg /
NK013(pa)013:210: phan nus zaba mo'i dabnga gi chu bo yisa //
NK013(pa)013:211: bdag rgyud sgrib pa'i dri ma legs 'khrud cing //
NK013(pa)013:212: rdo rje gsum zhal snying dbus 'dzum para shog /
NK013(pa)013:213: dbang dus gdan gsum dkyil 'khor bla mar bcas //
NK013(pa)013:214: dpang du btsugs nas srung bar khas blangs pa'i //
NK013(pa)013:215: rtsa ba yan lag sdomsa pa'i dam tshiga tshogs //
NK013(pa)013:216: snying dang miga lasa gcesa para srung bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:217: rmad byung rgyud sde'i rgya mtsho thosa bsam gru //
NK013(pa)013:218: brtson 'grus shes rab ba dan dkar po yis //
NK013(pa)013:219: legas para brgala te zab rgyas rin chen gling //
NK013(pa)013:220: sgoma pa'i nora bazanga bde blag rnyed para shog /
NK013(pa)013:221: ranga semas snang ba 'khrul pa'i gnyis chosa kun //
NK013(pa)013:222: snang dus nyid nas don dam mnyamsa pa nyid //
NK013(pa)013:223: dag pa raba 'byamsa kun rdzob rgyal ba'i dngos //
NK013(pa)013:224: rgyud don cha rkyen 'bras bu gdod ma nas //
NK013(pa)013:225: rang gnas rdo rje'i lus kyi 'khor lo drug /
NK013(pa)013:226: srog shing gsum dbus e wam ma ya'i gzugs //
NK013(pa)013:227: rtsa dbyibs 'od 'byung gzhi yi gasnga ba snying //
NK013(pa)013:228: rtogs pa'i gegs gyur glo bur sgrib bsal nas //
NK013(pa)013:229: bdena gnyis dbyer meda gzhi rtsa bral ba'i yul //
NK013(pa)013:230: dngos tshul gtan tshigas shes rab miga gisa gazhala //
NK013(pa)013:231: rtag chad gzung 'dzin rang rig don dam bden //
NK013(pa)013:232: bden gnyis ris phye'i dri bral de nyid rig /
NK013(pa)013:233: bzang ngan phyogs ris blo 'das gnyug ma'i gshis //
NK013(pa)013:234: lam dang rgyud kyi rgyu shes lta ba ni //
NK013(pa)013:235: tshangs la ma nor ngo sprod don mthong shog /
NK013(pa)013:236: bsam gtan 'gal rkyen tshogs spangs dbena pa'i gnas //
NK013(pa)013:237: yid 'ong sgra med zhi ba'i nags tshal du /
NK013(pa)013:239: / 'chi ba chos sku stong pa chena po yi //
NK013(pa)013:240: de ting rnal 'byor zab mos sbyong bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:241: log rtog mkha' dbyings chu skyes srid pa'i tshal //
NK013(pa)013:242: sdug bsngal myos pa'i semas cana yul med la //
NK013(pa)013:243: snying rje kun snang sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK013(pa)013:244: bar do longs spyod rdzogs skur sbyong bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:245: rnam rtog rlung gis ma bskyod ting nge 'dzin //
NK013(pa)013:246: sgron me rab gsal phra ragas cho ga gsum //
NK013(pa)013:247: rim gyis baskyed pas skye srid sbyong byed pa //
NK013(pa)013:248: phyag rgya gciga pa'i lhar snang brtan par shog /
NK013(pa)013:249: lam gyi gasnga snying rgyud don nyams blangs tshe //
NK013(pa)013:250: rgyal chen bzhi dang dpal ldan khro bo bcu'i /
NK013(pa)013:252: / 'khor gyis bskor ba'i zhe sdang rdo rje yis //
NK013(pa)013:253: bgegs 'joms phyogs bcings phyi nanga gasnga ba'i matshamas //
NK013(pa)013:254: bdag gi rnam rtog sems la legs bcad de //
NK013(pa)013:255: snod kyi snang ba 'og min gazhala med khang //
NK013(pa)013:256: bcud kyi sems can bcom ldan 'khora lo'i tshogas //
NK013(pa)013:257: gragsa pa gsung dang rtogsa pa blo 'das thugs //
NK013(pa)013:258: yid 'ong lha sku phyi yi rdo rje sems /
NK013(pa)013:259: mi shig thig le nang gi sgyu 'phrul te //
NK013(pa)013:260: rtog tshogs rang grol gasnga ba'i gasnga ba snying //
NK013(pa)013:261: ranga zhala mthong ba'i zung 'jug ting 'dzin 'phrul //
NK013(pa)013:262: dkyil 'khor tshom bu phyag rgya spros bcas la //
NK013(pa)013:263: rigs gcig rigs gsum rigs lnga sangs rgyas stong //
NK013(pa)013:264: nyi khri bzhi stong bdun khri drug stong sogs //
NK013(pa)013:265: rnam pa gsal zhing dag dran nga rgyal brtan //
NK013(pa)013:266: tshul dgus rab mdzes sangs rgyas zhi ba'i lha //
NK013(pa)013:267: gar dgus brjid ldan 'bar ba khrag 'thung gi //
NK013(pa)013:268: lha ru gsal ba bskyed pa'i rima pa dang //
NK013(pa)013:269: bde chen ye shes rdzogsa par mnyam sbyor bas /
NK013(pa)013:271: / 'dod yon thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)013:272: bde bar rol mthus tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs te //
NK013(pa)013:273: thal mal snang zhen sgrib 'di sgyu ma'i sku //
NK013(pa)013:274: ye shes kha sbyor gzugs su sbyong bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:275: gnas dus ston 'khor sgrub rdzas phun tshogs lnga //
NK013(pa)013:276: ma nyams cho ga lnga rdzogs yo byad ldan //
NK013(pa)013:277: yan lag lnga tshangs bsnyen dang nye bar bsnyen //
NK013(pa)013:278: sgrub pa sgrub chen +aa li k+aa li yis //
NK013(pa)013:279: tshoma bu tshogs kyi bsgrub pa yongs su rdzogs //
NK013(pa)013:280: thun mong gter sogs lu gu rgyud kyi las //
NK013(pa)013:281: rim pa dang po'i dngos grub brgyad bsgrub pas //
NK013(pa)013:282: zag med lam sbyong spyod pa mthar phyin shog /
NK013(pa)013:283: mkha' dkyil dwangs pa'i dbyings na nyi zla la //
NK013(pa)013:284: ye shesa rgyal po stangs dpyal ye sangs rgyas //
NK013(pa)013:285: bsgoms mthus skye gnas bzhi sbyongs gang snang kun //
NK013(pa)013:286: bsam mi khyab pa'i 'od gasla 'char bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:287: tshangas pa'i gansa su pad dkar ahham ltor //
NK013(pa)013:288: sangs rgyas kun 'dus bla ma rin po che //
NK013(pa)013:289: gnyis med sbyor ba'i bdud rtsis lus kun khyab //
NK013(pa)013:290: byin rlab dngosa grub ganda kyis dbang thob shog /
NK013(pa)013:291: khams drug ldan pa rdo rje'i lus 'di ni //
NK013(pa)013:292: gnad du bsnan na sangs rgyas tshe 'di la //
NK013(pa)013:293: thob phyir lus kyi gnas lugs la mkhas nas //
NK013(pa)013:294: stong ra'i gnad kyis dbu mar rlung zin shog /
NK013(pa)013:295: la la r+aa sa'i lcags kyus brtan g.yo'i dpal //
NK013(pa)013:296: d+hu ti'i pho brang nang du bsdu ba la //
NK013(pa)013:297: ngag gi rgyal po 'bru gsum rdor bzlas kyis //
NK013(pa)013:298: srog gi gnad mkhas rang snang dbang 'dus shog /
NK013(pa)013:299: sprul 'khor gtum mo'i thab khung kun rtog gi //
NK013(pa)013:300: bud shing bsregs pas sbar ba'i ye shes mes //
NK013(pa)013:301: bde chen 'khor lo'i ham dkar bzhu blugs rgyun //
NK013(pa)013:302: rtsol ba'i gnad kyis chos 'khor bde 'bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:303: dbu ma'i yar snar dwangs ma nyung 'bru tsam //
NK013(pa)013:304: dbyer med 'dres pa longs spyod 'khor lo'i bcud //
NK013(pa)013:305: drod kyis reg pas rtsa gang tshad meda bade //
NK013(pa)013:306: bde stong yid phrog mtshan dpe'i sku 'grub shog /
NK013(pa)013:307: snying ga'i dwangs ma'i 'od 'bar mgrin rten zhu //
NK013(pa)013:308: snying gar zhugs pas rgyu dang mi rgyu ba //
NK013(pa)013:309: kun byed las rlung nyer zhi zaga meda bade //
NK013(pa)013:310: bde stongs tshangs dbyangs rdo rje'i gsung thob shog /
NK013(pa)013:311: lte bas snying ga'i khams bskul de dang der //
NK013(pa)013:312: yongs khyab dran rtog zhi ba'i ti la ka /
NK013(pa)013:313: smra bsam brjod du med pa mchoga bade 'achara //
NK013(pa)013:314: bde stong mkhyen gnyis gzigs pa'i thugs brnyes shog /
NK013(pa)013:315: de ltar 'khor lo bzhi dbus mkha' sems dang //
NK013(pa)013:316: sa chu me rlung gcig 'dres dwangs ma'i rgyun //
NK013(pa)013:317: phra bas kun khyab nyer zhi'i bde ba rdzagas //
NK013(pa)013:318: yas bab sku bzhi'i lang tsho ngom par shog /
NK013(pa)013:319: snying ga'i zer gyis lte ba'i thig le bsdus //
NK013(pa)013:320: mgrin dang gtsug tor kun kyang kun gzhir thim /
NK013(pa)013:322: / 'dod lnga dbus kyi nam mkha'i ngang nyid du //
NK013(pa)013:323: mas brtan dag'a bzhi'i spros pa kun bsdus nas //
NK013(pa)013:324: don gyi 'od gsal stong pa chen po'i sbubs //
NK013(pa)013:325: dpe yi ye shes rdzogs pa'i rim pas sbyor //
NK013(pa)013:326: gya nom lhar zhen rtog pa'i 'gros bcom nas //
NK013(pa)013:327: zag med sgrib bral 'char bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK013(pa)013:328: de ltar me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK013(pa)013:329: stong phrag don gnyis rtsa ru bzhos pa'i bcud //
NK013(pa)013:330: snying la bstar bas bde stong mdza' na mo //
NK013(pa)013:331: thar pa'i dpyid du 'bral ba med gyur cig /
NK013(pa)013:332: skye 'gags gnas dmigs bral ba gdod ma'i gshis /
NK013(pa)013:334: / 'gro 'ong spros pas ma gos gnyug ma'i sems //
NK013(pa)013:335: kun bzang bsam mi khyab pa'i man ngag gis //
NK013(pa)013:336: ji bzhin rdzogs pa chen por rdzogs gyur cig /
NK013(pa)013:337: yid kyis lha sku stobs rdzogs rnam para smin //
NK013(pa)013:338: lus sems rdo rje'i gnas grub tshe la dabnga /
NK013(pa)013:340: / 'ja' lus g.yo ba med pa phyag rgya che //
NK013(pa)013:341: rtsol med lhun grub rig 'dzina bzhi bgrod nas //
NK013(pa)013:342: dpal ldan bla ma rnams kyi byin rlabs dang //
NK013(pa)013:343: gsang chen sgyu d+r+wa'i zab lam myur khyad dang //
NK013(pa)013:344: rtse gcig sgom pa rnam par dag pa'i stobs //
NK013(pa)013:345: mthong ba'i chos la dpal ldan rdo rje'i sems //
NK013(pa)013:346: don gyi gsang snying mthar 'bras mngon du byas //
NK013(pa)013:347: rdo rje'i ting 'dzin 'khrul pa'i tshogs kun 'joms //
NK013(pa)013:348: nyi shu rtsa lnga mi zad gter chen brdol //
NK013(pa)013:349: he ru kahdapala myur du brnyes gyur cig /
NK013(pa)013:350: go 'phang mchog de tshe 'dir ma thob kyang /
NK013(pa)013:352: / 'chi tshe bla ma kun bzang 'khor bcas kyis //
NK013(pa)013:353: yid 'ong mchod sprin snyan pa'i rol mo'i sgra //
NK013(pa)013:354: ngo mtshar ltas bzang mang pos bsu bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:355: de tshe 'chi ba chos sku'i 'od gsal las //
NK013(pa)013:356: bar do longs spyod rdzogs pas skye gnas kun //
NK013(pa)013:357: sprul sku ngo mtshar sgyu ma'i sprin dkar po //
NK013(pa)013:358: sems nyid bde chen mkha' las ldang bar shog /
NK013(pa)013:359: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs kyi bcud phyung zhing //
NK013(pa)013:360: rgyal sras kun gyi gus pas phyag byas pa //
NK013(pa)013:361: rab 'byams zhing na gsung gi gsang ba kun //
NK013(pa)013:362: spro ba'i gzhir gyur rgyud rgyal 'dis mtshon te //
NK013(pa)013:363: gsang chen rgyud sde'i bstan pa rin po che /
NK013(pa)013:365: / 'jig rten khams su yun ring gnas pa dang //
NK013(pa)013:366: der 'dzin rnams kyi bzheng don skyongs ba la //
NK013(pa)013:367: gnas yul mkha' 'gro kun gyis grogs mdzad cing //
NK013(pa)013:368: brgyud gsum rig 'dzin bla ma'i thugs kyis dgongs //
NK013(pa)013:369: snang srid dam can dregs pas bka' la nyan //
NK013(pa)013:370: rang rgyud smin cing gzhan rgyud grol ba yi //
NK013(pa)013:371: bkra shis grags pa'i ba dan kun khyab shog /
NK013(pa)013:372: ces pa 'adi'ang mkhas grub chen po'i lam rim 'grel
NK013(pa)013:373: chen dbur bzhugs brgyud 'debs la kha skong gi sho
NK013(pa)013:377: rim gsum la sogs pa las 'byung ba'i dpal sgyu
NK013(pa)013:378: 'phrul dra ba'i lam tshang la ma nor ba smon
NK013(pa)013:379: lam du bsdebs te sbyor ba po ni /
NK013(pa)013:380: rgyud kyi rgyal po la shes nas dad pa thob
NK013(pa)013:381: pa'i rig 'dzin gyi btsun pa chos kyi rgya mtsho
NK013(pa)013:382: bstan pa'i nyi ma dpal bzang po ste /
NK013(pa)013:383: 'dis kyang rang gzhan sems can thams cad zab mo'i
NK013(pa)013:384: lam 'di la brten nas khyab bdag rdo rje sems
